        </a>
        <a href="/guides/split-keyboard" class="group block bg-white text-bp-dark text-center py-3 md:py-4 font-bold text-sm md:text-base hover:bg-white/90 transition-colors border-t-2 border-white/20">
          See Full Guide <span class="inline-block transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1">→</span>
